OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early mist and fog patches
OL,6,Fsoon clearing, then a fine day ahead
OL,7,Fwith warm sunny spells. The sunshine
OL,8,Fmay turn hazy at times this afternoon.
OL,9,FVery mild for the time of year with
OL,10,Flight winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FTurning cloudier this evening
OL,13,Fand overnight with a few spots of
OL,14,Frain, more so by dawn. Winds staying
OL,15,Flight and temperatures holding up
OL,16,Fabove freezing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
