OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA cloudier day compared to
OL,6,FThursday with outbreaks of rain
OL,7,Fdeveloping on and off through the
OL,8,Fmorning and afternoon, most of which
OL,9,Fwill be light. Feeling cooler, though
OL,10,Flight winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,13,FOccasional patchy rain and drizzle in
OL,14,Fplaces, but mostly dry albeit often
OL,15,Fcloudy. Cloud breaking at times to
OL,16,Fgive some sunshine. Temperatures
OL,17,Fcloser to average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
